{
  "stem": "21013.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And from the time I was six years old, I was very interested in politics-- not only me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "All the other children were too, because we were practicing with gas masks in-- in first grade.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we learned how to put out incendiary bombs.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There were revolutions and putsches and civil war and all kinds of strife, so it was a very interesting childhood.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And Hitler came in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I mean, we had so many-- we had a chancellor assassinated in the parliament.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That was Dollfuss, the very short chancellor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, all I know is that he was assassinated by someone who disguised himself as a cleaning person and assassinated him.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then his heir was a young man who used to be minister of education, by the name of Kurt von Schuschnigg, whom I subsequently met at a cocktail party in Highland Park, Illinois.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Schuschnigg was head of-- Austria was a republic after the war.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was a Social Democratic republic.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's not Socialist in the sense of Socialist here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was Social Democratic, which was milder.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was to the left, but not as far left as a Socialist.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "After Dollfuss was assassinated [SIGHS] and Schuschnigg came in, it-- Austria became Christian Socialists, which was the religious right.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would say maybe '35, '36.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And my father, who held many honorary positions-- he had a card printed at one time where he was president or board member of 26 different organizations, including his professional organization, the dealers of antiques.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when Schuschnigg came in, he got one letter after the other kicking him out of all his jobs because he was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the rumblings of National Socialism came long before the Anschluss.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
